-- PDG Realty Gains on 53 Percent Surge in Second-Quarter Contracted Sales
-- Alexander Ragir
-- 2010-07-13T21:00:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/pdg-realty-gains-on-53-percent-surge-in-second-quarter-contracted-sales.html

          
          
             PDG Realty SA Empreendimentos &
Participacoes , Brazil’s third-biggest homebuilder by revenue,
gained the most in a week after saying its second-quarter
contracted sales jumped 53 percent from a year ago.  
 PDG gained 4 percent to 17.20 reais, the most since July 6.
PDG reported sales of 1.56 billion reais ($887.7 million).  
 “The numbers were strong, and we expect a positive
reaction,” JPMorgan Chase & Co. analyst Adriana E. Huerta wrote
in a note to clients.  
